-simple implementation of a counter with an increment decrement and clear button 
increment and decrement function in counter.js
clear function in clear.js

-setting up eslintrc.json-including changes to existing rules:eslintrc.json
-using eslint ignore file to exclude gulpfile:eslintignore
-using commands to ignore files while linting:clear.js
-using commands to ignore particular line in:counter.js
-configuring a gulp file to run eslint task:gulpfile.js

dependencies used:
eslint
gulp
gulp-eslint
